  "scripts/extract_hol4.jl: remove narrow 7-keyword tactic gate; new hol4_tactic_names helper; add Triviality / (Co)Inductive / Q.prove / Q.store_thm patterns; Definition tolerates [simp] + Termination blocks (commit aa88649)",
  "scripts/extract_tptp.jl: only skip when conjecture AND axioms AND includes are all empty; include-only files now carry their include list as context (commit 64d8cb4)",
